            ("304B", "Dowry death", "Where the death of a woman is caused by any burns or bodily injury or occurs under abnormal circumstances within seven years of marriage, and it is shown that soon before her death she was subjected to cruelty or harassment by her husband or relatives for, or in connection with, any demand for dowry, such death shall be called 'dowry death'.", "If a wife dies within 7 years of marriage due to burns or injury, and was harassed over dowry demands, it is 'dowry death' punishable by 7 years to life imprisonment.", "திருமணமான 7 ஆண்டுகளுக்குள் மனைவி வரதட்சணை கொடுமையினால் மடிந்தால், அது வரதட்சணை மரணம் என கணக்கிடப்படும்; 7 ஆண்டுகள் முதல் ஆயுள் வரை சிறை தண்டனை.", "यदि विवाह के 7 साल के भीतर पत्नी की मृत्यु दहेज उत्पीड़न से होती है, तो इसे 'दहेज हत्या' माना जाएगा; 7 साल से आजीवन कारावास तक की सजा।", "Minimum 7 years imprisonment, up to life imprisonment", "high"),
            ("376", "Punishment for rape", "Whoever commits rape shall be punished with rigorous imprisonment of either description for a term which shall not be less than ten years, but which may extend to imprisonment for life, and shall also be liable to fine.", "Rape is punishable with rigorous imprisonment of at least 10 years and can extend to life imprisonment. The victim can also receive compensation.", "கற்பழிப்பு குற்றத்திற்கு குறைந்தது 10 ஆண்டு கடுமையான சிறைத்தண்டனை, ஆயுள் தண்டனை வரை நீட்டிக்கப்படலாம். பாதிக்கப்பட்டவருக்கு இழப்பீடும் வழங்கப்படலாம்.", "बलात्कार के लिए कम से कम 10 साल की कठोर कारावास सजा है जो आजीवन हो सकती है।", "Rigorous imprisonment minimum 10 years to life, and fine", "high"),
